b_paragraph\" >玩家可以按壓方向鍵，進行左右的水平移動</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/583e3db0c69ebb787ffaddd8fe0576ae.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=466 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/583e3db0c69ebb787ffaddd8fe0576ae.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/583e3db0c69ebb787ffaddd8fe0576ae.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>使用技能躲避危險</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >按下對應的按鈕後，即可對應角色技能，來閃避Boss的攻擊。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/171376600d094bdac38731e5336a9e76.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=604 height=466 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/171376600d094bdac38731e5336a9e76.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/171376600d094bdac38731e5336a9e76.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>釋放大招，攻擊Boss</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家消耗當下的所獲得所有蓄力值，對敵方角色進行攻擊，減少其生命值。釋放能量進行攻擊時，會有短暫的無敵效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/dcc0efdc3220163fd89cd99a74fda090.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=604 height=466 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/dcc0efdc3220163fd89cd99a74fda090.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/dcc0efdc3220163fd89cd99a74fda090.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/3025993a47ce6d57534ab83b6c0818ca.avif?t=1745896769\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>像素風的人物與關卡設計</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本次遊戲所採用的美術，將結合日本遊戲JRPG立繪風格，與像素畫風結合，每一個關卡的地圖場景、地板機制，都是全新設計，帶給玩家不重複的關卡體驗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>懷舊玩法融合新要素</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作的核心遊戲機制，參考自一款日本小遊戲「小朋友下樓梯」改良的動作遊戲。並新增了許多新元素，包含：特殊機制地板、滯空技、Boss攻擊技等。帶給玩家具有挑戰性的關卡體驗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>精心設計的BOSS與關卡</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲關卡內含精心設計的BOSS戰，每個BOSS都有獨特的造型和攻擊手段，琳瑯滿目的攻擊，將要挑戰玩家的反應能力。不同角色擁有不同的專屬被動與特殊技能，通關後可解鎖已經擊敗的Boss角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>精美的像素點陣與日文配音</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正式版遊戲中，將加入更多的像素動圖，並且在某些故事劇情中，將加入專業的日文聲優配音，讓遊戲體驗更有臨場感！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/e6ddff0d7004267d286ca396519c8b97.avif?t=1745896769\" width=616 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/fd65383f733bec8003fdb3449e046710.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/fd65383f733bec8003fdb3449e046710.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/fd65383f733bec8003fdb3449e046710.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>CV:伊ヶ崎綾香</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>統御天空塔的女王，天生擁有強大的魔力寶具「冰霜寶珠」，性格單純善良，不討厭人類，常常得意忘形。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/f756cd9c6a0b1bbf741e792e7b9073ec.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/f756cd9c6a0b1bbf741e792e7b9073ec.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>CV:花城かざり<br>賭性堅強，不賭到贏絕不放棄。性格調皮搗蛋，喜歡惡作劇。作為賭場的管理者，有時也會露出冷酷無情的一面。</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/2d8f142e76abadbea39c3843b5ed7f84.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/2d8f142e76abadbea39c3843b5ed7f84.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/2d8f142e76abadbea39c3843b5ed7f84.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>CV:大宗たゆゆ<br>表面上是溫柔的大姊姊，身體呈半透明狀，對於她喜歡的對象會產生極大的照顧慾。 </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>體型與正常人相似，但如果吸了水則可以無限增大。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/1be9be4376d445e2e1a061acf3692475.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/1be9be4376d445e2e1a061acf3692475.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/1be9be4376d445e2e1a061acf3692475.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>CV:財木 桜<br>秉持著家族的使命，守護著華楓庭園，個性看似嚴厲，卻有著純真的心靈。喜歡小孩子。</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/76d33624fa315e22481842b929045d1b.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/76d33624fa315e22481842b929045d1b.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/76d33624fa315e22481842b929045d1b.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>CV:園宮さつき<br>穿著連衣帽外套，平常都會用帽子把頭蓋住，喜歡唱反調，容易害羞。討厭自己的金屬尾巴。</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/5165a6c611c0b100b3e809623b589c8c.avif?t=1745896769\" width=616 height=72 /></span>在遙遠的異世界裡，駕著飛行器的主角-塔瓦羅某一天飛行時，突然遭遇風暴而失事，墜落的飛行器撞擊天空塔塔頂的水晶宮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >天空塔是位於大陸中央，充滿魔物與陷阱的高塔，而水晶宮則是統治天空塔的中樞。身為水晶宮領主的芙洛薇亞，此刻正好在把玩控制整座水晶宮的冰霜寶珠……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由於塔瓦羅造成的撞擊，芙洛薇亞不小心失手讓寶珠往塔底掉落，天空塔的魔物因此失去控制，而開始爆走。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >為了幫助芙洛薇亞撿回丟失的寶珠，塔瓦羅利用自身經驗，指點芙洛薇亞降落技巧，兩人一起結伴往下層邁進。面對陷阱密布的樓層、不懷好意的魔物領主們。一場充滿未知與挑戰的旅程開始了……</p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/0ee76fcd65714593023a3fa550a1b9c3.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/0ee76fcd65714593023a3fa550a1b9c3.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/0ee76fcd65714593023a3fa550a1b9c3.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/f7f8866b60e1eb0b21a318488595f1b1.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/f7f8866b60e1eb0b21a318488595f1b1.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/f7f8866b60e1eb0b21a318488595f1b1.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/4f65d27b47f61a5fdb1e758f5a955efe.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/8fafdf31f54b3e6c1706b03b738cee5d.avif?t=1745896769\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>左右移動、閃避陷阱</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可以按壓方向鍵，進行左右的水平移動</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/583e3db0c69ebb787ffaddd8fe0576ae.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=466 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/583e3db0c69ebb787ffaddd8fe0576ae.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/583e3db0c69ebb787ffaddd8fe0576ae.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>使用技能躲避危險</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >按下對應的按鈕後，即可對應角色技能，來閃避Boss的攻擊。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/171376600d094bdac38731e5336a9e76.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=604 height=466 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/171376600d094bdac38731e5336a9e76.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/171376600d094bdac38731e5336a9e76.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>釋放大招，攻擊Boss</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家消耗當下的所獲得所有蓄力值，對敵方角色進行攻擊，減少其生命值。釋放能量進行攻擊時，會有短暫的無敵效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/dcc0efdc3220163fd89cd99a74fda090.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=604 height=466 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/dcc0efdc3220163fd89cd99a74fda090.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/dcc0efdc3220163fd89cd99a74fda090.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/3025993a47ce6d57534ab83b6c0818ca.avif?t=1745896769\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>像素風的人物與關卡設計</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本次遊戲所採用的美術，將結合日本遊戲JRPG立繪風格，與像素畫風結合，每一個關卡的地圖場景、地板機制，都是全新設計，帶給玩家不重複的關卡體驗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>懷舊玩法融合新要素</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作的核心遊戲機制，參考自一款日本小遊戲「小朋友下樓梯」改良的動作遊戲。並新增了許多新元素，包含：特殊機制地板、滯空技、Boss攻擊技等。帶給玩家具有挑戰性的關卡體驗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>精心設計的BOSS與關卡</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲關卡內含精心設計的BOSS戰，每個BOSS都有獨特的造型和攻擊手段，琳瑯滿目的攻擊，將要挑戰玩家的反應能力。不同角色擁有不同的專屬被動與特殊技能，通關後可解鎖已經擊敗的Boss角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>精美的像素點陣與日文配音</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正式版遊戲中，將加入更多的像素動圖，並且在某些故事劇情中，將加入專業的日文聲優配音，讓遊戲體驗更有臨場感！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/e6ddff0d7004267d286ca396519c8b97.avif?t=1745896769\" width=616 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/fd65383f733bec8003fdb3449e046710.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/fd65383f733bec8003fdb3449e046710.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/fd65383f733bec8003fdb3449e046710.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>CV:伊ヶ崎綾香</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>統御天空塔的女王，天生擁有強大的魔力寶具「冰霜寶珠」，性格單純善良，不討厭人類，常常得意忘形。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/f756cd9c6a0b1bbf741e792e7b9073ec.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/f756cd9c6a0b1bbf741e792e7b9073ec.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>CV:花城かざり<br>賭性堅強，不賭到贏絕不放棄。性格調皮搗蛋，喜歡惡作劇。作為賭場的管理者，有時也會露出冷酷無情的一面。</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/2d8f142e76abadbea39c3843b5ed7f84.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/2d8f142e76abadbea39c3843b5ed7f84.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/2d8f142e76abadbea39c3843b5ed7f84.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>CV:大宗たゆゆ<br>表面上是溫柔的大姊姊，身體呈半透明狀，對於她喜歡的對象會產生極大的照顧慾。 </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>體型與正常人相似，但如果吸了水則可以無限增大。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/1be9be4376d445e2e1a061acf3692475.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/1be9be4376d445e2e1a061acf3692475.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/1be9be4376d445e2e1a061acf3692475.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>CV:財木 桜<br>秉持著家族的使命，守護著華楓庭園，個性看似嚴厲，卻有著純真的心靈。喜歡小孩子。</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/76d33624fa315e22481842b929045d1b.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/76d33624fa315e22481842b929045d1b.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/76d33624fa315e22481842b929045d1b.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>CV:園宮さつき<br>穿著連衣帽外套，平常都會用帽子把頭蓋住，喜歡唱反調，容易害羞。討厭自己的金屬尾巴。</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/5165a6c611c0b100b3e809623b589c8c.avif?t=1745896769\" width=616 height=72 /></span>在遙遠的異世界裡，駕著飛行器的主角-塔瓦羅某一天飛行時，突然遭遇風暴而失事，墜落的飛行器撞擊天空塔塔頂的水晶宮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >天空塔是位於大陸中央，充滿魔物與陷阱的高塔，而水晶宮則是統治天空塔的中樞。身為水晶宮領主的芙洛薇亞，此刻正好在把玩控制整座水晶宮的冰霜寶珠……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由於塔瓦羅造成的撞擊，芙洛薇亞不小心失手讓寶珠往塔底掉落，天空塔的魔物因此失去控制，而開始爆走。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >為了幫助芙洛薇亞撿回丟失的寶珠，塔瓦羅利用自身經驗，指點芙洛薇亞降落技巧，兩人一起結伴往下層邁進。面對陷阱密布的樓層、不懷好意的魔物領主們。一場充滿未知與挑戰的旅程開始了……</p>", "short_description": "《下來啊！冰鳥》是一款融合經典下樓梯與像素風格的快節奏動作成人遊戲，你和失去魔力的美少女魔物女王一起結伴往下層探索，尋找失去的寶珠。面對陷阱密布的樓層、性感又不懷好意魔物領主們，一場充滿未知與挑戰的旅程開始了…", "supported_languages": "英文, 繁體中文, 日文, 簡體中文, 韓文", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1745896769", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/c1ae4109fdaed1651b4a9e1d4b771e0a9f5e37ce/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1745896769", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/c1ae4109fdaed1651b4a9e1d4b771e0a9f5e37ce/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1745896769", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows 7 64bit OS<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Core i3<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 2 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> HD Graphics<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 2 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10 64bit OS<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Core i5<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> HD Graphics<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 4 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "developers": ["F Project"], "publishers": ["Alice Publication", "Eternal Alice Media"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 19800, "final": 19800, "discount_percent": 0, "initial_formatted": "", "final_formatted": "NT$ 198"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 1, "description": "多人"}, {"id": 49, "description": "玩家對戰"}, {"id": 37, "description": "共享 / 分割螢幕玩家對戰"}, {"id": 9, "description": "合作"}, {"id": 39, "description": "共享 / 分割螢幕合作"}, {"id": 24, "description": "共享／分割螢幕"}, {"id": 22, "description": "Steam 成就"}, {"id": 28, "description": "完全支援控制器"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam 雲端"}, {"id": 44, "description": "遠端同樂"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "1", "description": "動作"}, {"id": "25", "description": "冒險"}, {"id": "4", "description": "休閒"}, {"id": "23", "description": "獨立製作"}, {"id": "3", "description": "角色扮演"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2024 年 11 月 21 日"}}}}, "us": {"2685500": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Falling with Ice Phoenix!", "steam_appid": 2685500, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/0ee76fcd65714593023a3fa550a1b9c3.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/0ee76fcd65714593023a3fa550a1b9c3.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/0ee76fcd65714593023a3fa550a1b9c3.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/f7f8866b60e1eb0b21a318488595f1b1.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/f7f8866b60e1eb0b21a318488595f1b1.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/f7f8866b60e1eb0b21a318488595f1b1.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/4f65d27b47f61a5fdb1e758f5a955efe.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=338 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/f4085e6ada0debe59da25a084e347584.avif?t=1745896769\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Horizontal Movement</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players can press the left and right arrow keys to move horizontally.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/583e3db0c69ebb787ffaddd8fe0576ae.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=466 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/583e3db0c69ebb787ffaddd8fe0576ae.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/583e3db0c69ebb787ffaddd8fe0576ae.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Use skills to avoid danger</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pressing the corresponding button allows you to activate the skill to dodge the Boss' attack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/171376600d094bdac38731e5336a9e76.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=604 height=466 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/171376600d094bdac38731e5336a9e76.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/171376600d094bdac38731e5336a9e76.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Release the ult and attack the Boss</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players use up all their current energy to launch an attack against enemy characters, reducing their health. When releasing energy to attack, there is a brief period of invincibility.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/dcc0efdc3220163fd89cd99a74fda090.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=604 height=466 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/dcc0efdc3220163fd89cd99a74fda090.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/dcc0efdc3220163fd89cd99a74fda090.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/46068d4b8585d2faad578b34b73884bb.avif?t=1745896769\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pixel Art Style Characters and Level Design</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game will feature a blend of Japanese JRPG-style illustrations and pixel art, offering players a unique and non-repetitive experience with newly designed maps, scenes, and floor mechanisms in each level!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Blending Nostalgic Gameplay with New Elements</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The core gameplay mechanics of this game are inspired by a Japanese action game called &quot;NS-SHAFT.&quot; Our game features many new elements, including special floor mechanisms, mid-air techniques, and boss attacks, providing players with a challenging level experience!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Carefully Designed Bosses and Levels</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game includes meticulously designed boss battles, with each boss featuring unique appearances and attack patterns. These diverse attacks will challenge players' reaction times. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To face these powerful bosses, players can choose from different characters and items, each with their own passive abilities and special skills. Completing levels unlocks the defeated boss characters as playable characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Enhanced Pixel Art and Voice Acting</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The full version of the game will include more pixel animations and Japanese voice acting in select story scenes to enhance the immersive experience!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/e71f5f1672001d2f0f0f30e7fd36f15c.avif?t=1745896769\" width=616 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/1f3b8a3e5d7b82065ec54aa71c3b23f0.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/1f3b8a3e5d7b82065ec54aa71c3b23f0.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/1f3b8a3e5d7b82065ec54aa71c3b23f0.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>CV:伊ヶ崎綾香</strong><br><strong>The queen of the Sky Tower, born with the powerful magical artifact, the &quot;Frost Orb.&quot;</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>She is pure-hearted and kind, doesn't dislike humans, and often gets carried away.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/fbad4643cbf08ac9c01603031d58f889.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/fbad4643cbf08ac9c01603031d58f889.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>CV:花城かざり</strong><br><strong>A determined gambler who never gives up until she wins. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Playful and mischievous, she enjoys pranks. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>As the casino manager, she sometimes shows a cold and ruthless side.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/6bfa0cd3f5021beef075dc57feacf721.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/6bfa0cd3f5021beef075dc57feacf721.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/6bfa0cd3f5021beef075dc57feacf721.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>CV:大宗たゆゆ</strong><br><strong>Appears as a gentle older sister with a semi-transparent body. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>She has a strong desire to care for those she likes. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Her body is similar in size to a normal human, but she can grow infinitely if she absorbs water.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/847366ebeb404beb83363da104e71ff1.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/847366ebeb404beb83363da104e71ff1.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/847366ebeb404beb83363da104e71ff1.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>CV:財木 桜</strong><br><strong>She upholds her family's mission to protect the Maple Garden.  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Although she seems strict, she has a pure heart and loves children.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/df828cebaf7d919b4e0bab4987e590eb.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/df828cebaf7d919b4e0bab4987e590eb.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/df828cebaf7d919b4e0bab4987e590eb.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>CV:園宮さつき</strong><br><strong>Wears a hooded coat, usually keeping her head covered. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>She enjoys being contrary, is easily embarrassed, and dislikes her metallic tail.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/5d8a75582fd0fd5a866a610c7878dcb3.avif?t=1745896769\" width=616 height=72 /></span>In a distant realm, the protagonist Tavaro was piloting his aircraft when he suddenly encountered a storm and crashed into the crystal palace atop the Sky Tower.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Sky Tower is located at the central region of the continent, a towering structure teeming with monsters and traps. The crystal palace serves as the central hub ruling over the Sky Tower. At that moment, Frostia, the lord of the crystal palace, was fiddling with the frost orb that controls the entire palace...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a result of Tavaro's collision, Frostia accidentally dropped the orb towards the base of the tower, causing the monsters in the Sky Tower to lose control and go berserk.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To help Frostia retrieve the lost orb, Tavaro used his experience to guide her in landing techniques, and they journeyed downward together. They faced trap-laden floors and malevolent monster lords. Thus, a journey filled with unknown challenges began...</p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/0ee76fcd65714593023a3fa550a1b9c3.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/0ee76fcd65714593023a3fa550a1b9c3.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/0ee76fcd65714593023a3fa550a1b9c3.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/f7f8866b60e1eb0b21a318488595f1b1.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/f7f8866b60e1eb0b21a318488595f1b1.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/f7f8866b60e1eb0b21a318488595f1b1.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/4f65d27b47f61a5fdb1e758f5a955efe.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=338 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/f4085e6ada0debe59da25a084e347584.avif?t=1745896769\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Horizontal Movement</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players can press the left and right arrow keys to move horizontally.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/583e3db0c69ebb787ffaddd8fe0576ae.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=466 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/583e3db0c69ebb787ffaddd8fe0576ae.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/583e3db0c69ebb787ffaddd8fe0576ae.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Use skills to avoid danger</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pressing the corresponding button allows you to activate the skill to dodge the Boss' attack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/171376600d094bdac38731e5336a9e76.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=604 height=466 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/171376600d094bdac38731e5336a9e76.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/171376600d094bdac38731e5336a9e76.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Release the ult and attack the Boss</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players use up all their current energy to launch an attack against enemy characters, reducing their health. When releasing energy to attack, there is a brief period of invincibility.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/dcc0efdc3220163fd89cd99a74fda090.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=604 height=466 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/dcc0efdc3220163fd89cd99a74fda090.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/dcc0efdc3220163fd89cd99a74fda090.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/46068d4b8585d2faad578b34b73884bb.avif?t=1745896769\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pixel Art Style Characters and Level Design</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game will feature a blend of Japanese JRPG-style illustrations and pixel art, offering players a unique and non-repetitive experience with newly designed maps, scenes, and floor mechanisms in each level!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Blending Nostalgic Gameplay with New Elements</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The core gameplay mechanics of this game are inspired by a Japanese action game called &quot;NS-SHAFT.&quot; Our game features many new elements, including special floor mechanisms, mid-air techniques, and boss attacks, providing players with a challenging level experience!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Carefully Designed Bosses and Levels</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game includes meticulously designed boss battles, with each boss featuring unique appearances and attack patterns. These diverse attacks will challenge players' reaction times. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To face these powerful bosses, players can choose from different characters and items, each with their own passive abilities and special skills. Completing levels unlocks the defeated boss characters as playable characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Enhanced Pixel Art and Voice Acting</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The full version of the game will include more pixel animations and Japanese voice acting in select story scenes to enhance the immersive experience!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/e71f5f1672001d2f0f0f30e7fd36f15c.avif?t=1745896769\" width=616 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/1f3b8a3e5d7b82065ec54aa71c3b23f0.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/1f3b8a3e5d7b82065ec54aa71c3b23f0.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/1f3b8a3e5d7b82065ec54aa71c3b23f0.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>CV:伊ヶ崎綾香</strong><br><strong>The queen of the Sky Tower, born with the powerful magical artifact, the &quot;Frost Orb.&quot;</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>She is pure-hearted and kind, doesn't dislike humans, and often gets carried away.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/fbad4643cbf08ac9c01603031d58f889.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/fbad4643cbf08ac9c01603031d58f889.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>CV:花城かざり</strong><br><strong>A determined gambler who never gives up until she wins. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Playful and mischievous, she enjoys pranks. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>As the casino manager, she sometimes shows a cold and ruthless side.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/6bfa0cd3f5021beef075dc57feacf721.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/6bfa0cd3f5021beef075dc57feacf721.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/6bfa0cd3f5021beef075dc57feacf721.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>CV:大宗たゆゆ</strong><br><strong>Appears as a gentle older sister with a semi-transparent body. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>She has a strong desire to care for those she likes. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Her body is similar in size to a normal human, but she can grow infinitely if she absorbs water.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/847366ebeb404beb83363da104e71ff1.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/847366ebeb404beb83363da104e71ff1.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/847366ebeb404beb83363da104e71ff1.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>CV:財木 桜</strong><br><strong>She upholds her family's mission to protect the Maple Garden.  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Although she seems strict, she has a pure heart and loves children.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/df828cebaf7d919b4e0bab4987e590eb.poster.avif?t=1745896769\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/df828cebaf7d919b4e0bab4987e590eb.webm?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/df828cebaf7d919b4e0bab4987e590eb.mp4?t=1745896769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>CV:園宮さつき</strong><br><strong>Wears a hooded coat, usually keeping her head covered. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>She enjoys being contrary, is easily embarrassed, and dislikes her metallic tail.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/extras/5d8a75582fd0fd5a866a610c7878dcb3.avif?t=1745896769\" width=616 height=72 /></span>In a distant realm, the protagonist Tavaro was piloting his aircraft when he suddenly encountered a storm and crashed into the crystal palace atop the Sky Tower.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Sky Tower is located at the central region of the continent, a towering structure teeming with monsters and traps. The crystal palace serves as the central hub ruling over the Sky Tower. At that moment, Frostia, the lord of the crystal palace, was fiddling with the frost orb that controls the entire palace...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a result of Tavaro's collision, Frostia accidentally dropped the orb towards the base of the tower, causing the monsters in the Sky Tower to lose control and go berserk.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To help Frostia retrieve the lost orb, Tavaro used his experience to guide her in landing techniques, and they journeyed downward together. They faced trap-laden floors and malevolent monster lords. Thus, a journey filled with unknown challenges began...</p>", "short_description": "Falling with Ice Phoenix! combining the classic gravity fall platformer, sprited and high-octane action game, you and the cutie monster girls venture downwards to find the lost orb, facing traps and sexy monster lords ahead, an exciting adventure to the unknown lays ahead...", "supported_languages": "English, Traditional Chinese, Japanese, Simplified Chinese, Korean", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/header.jpg?t=1745896769", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/59e1eb6b1b7d9859e8563bd3a007c4f5e48c8394/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1745896769", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685500/59e1eb6b1b7d9859e8563bd3a007c4f5e48c8394/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1745896769", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS *:</strong> Windows 7 64bit OS<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Core i3<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 2 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> HD Graphics<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 2 GB available space</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Windows 10 64bit OS<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Core i5<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 4 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> HD Graphics<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 4 GB available space</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "developers": ["F Project"], "publishers": ["Alice Publication", 